  "description": {
    "zh": "终点线到了，伙计！开玩笑的，我们只是快要结束这个特定的章节了，毕竟这些就是我们能搞到的所有突击步枪了。你还没有收集完所有它们的数据，一些非常特殊的仍然留下。主要是大口径步枪，但也有些非常稀有的枪。\n\n很多人质疑其中一些武器是如何最终出现在俄罗斯的，更不用说塔科夫了。我不得不对这些枪做些研究，很迷人，即使在它们被制造的国家，它们似乎也极其罕见，特别是SIG SPEAR，它确实是一把非常有趣的枪。尽管它很稀有，但你们操作员似乎很喜欢它，我猜是因为口径和射速，对吧？好吧，那你做你的工作，我处理文书工作，拿着清单，因为SPEAR不是你唯一会使用的工具。\n\n祝你好运，捍卫者，这次不会有任何样品了。",
    "en": "End of the line partner! Just kidding, we're only closing this specific chapter soon, after all those would be all assault rifles we can get our hands on. You haven't collected data on all of them yet, some of the very special ones are still left. Mostly high caliber rifles but also some very rare guns\n\nLots of people question how some of these weapons ended up in Russia, let alone Tarkov. I had to do some research on those guns, fascinating, even in the countries they were made they seem to be incredibly rare, the SIG SPEAR specifically, it's a very interesting gun indeed. Despite it's rarity, you operators seem to love it, I'm guessing it's because of the caliber and firerate, right? Alright then, you do your job, I handle the paperwork, have the list, because the SPEAR ain't the only tool you will use.\n\nGood luck out there champion, there won't be any samples this time."
  },
